Parameters

  • name – the workflow name

  • project_id – the uuid of project which contains this workflow

  • properties – the workflow properties

  • create_time – create time represented as milliseconds since epoch.

  • update_time – update time represented as milliseconds since epoch.

  • uuid – uuid in database
